At the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Hortense's population was 252. Among its population, 92.46% of was non-Hispanic white, 0.40% Native American, 3.57% multiracial, and 3.57% Hispanic or Latino of any race.<ref name="2020CensusP2" />

